What you need to know:

Two Kenyans, former Paris Marathon champion Paul Lonyangata and Elisha Rotich, are among 12 foreign athletes invited for the race that is classified as Bronze Label by the World AthleticsRotich said each athlete is training in their rooms and organisers are taking good care of themLonyangata said he is looking forward to a good race despite the strict measures to curb the spread of the virus